br>The roleplay reasoning behind this massive damage shield is simple. As a 60 paladin you are the elite among your diety's worshippers. The god/dess simply will not allow you to be struck with out some sort of &quot;Divine Retribution&quot; to the creature that would dare strike his/her favored champion.<br><br>This would give us a shot at being MT for some melee intensive mobs because if we are kept alive for the duration of the disc the amount of damage done is astronomical. It is balanced because it will take clerics far more mana to keep us alive than it would a warrior, so chaining together paladins as MT would quickly cause the clerics CH cycle to break. And the long refresh time would limit the usage dramatically, while still giving us a viable tool, and add a new strategy to the game revolving around the paladin class. <br><br>Ok, my excitement is gone now. Please feel free to shoot this idea down quickly. <p><bold><a href = "http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=101014">Varner Rapscallion</a> <br>58 Knight of Brell<br> Master Brewer, Fletcher, Potter, Baker</bold></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uriggorsmortus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RiggorsMortus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 146<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/6/02 10:08:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14741.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Off the wall suggestion for a 60 Disc</span><hr size=1> 250 to 500 pts total or for 20-30 secs (5k to 15k total)<br><br>either way it won't happen<br